metadata.name: Alien Scum Fleet #1
metadata.description: Alien Scum Fleet is an NFT collection of 6,969 NFTs on the Ethereum blockchain who make up a tough and incredibly effective military faction that was formerly based on planet Gargaldeez. Despite our militarization, however, we are a largely peaceful faction who only fight in self-defense. While the Fleet trains by day and guzzles $SLATT by night, our hearts are ever-set on rebuilding their fleet in the metaverse.
